{"tid":1430954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[對唔住，我一世不再做標題黨] 關於民間記者會我有嘢想講，我地需要新的文宣手法去散開記者會上所講嘅嘢","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:58:01.000Z","uid":284531,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ab88ff46e6659ee0a95e56067d40f9f37a099e2f","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:12:29.000Z","msg":"對唔住，細佬反省過，一世唔會再做標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />懇求大家原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完巴打建議，決定重開一篇文。請各位無視我上一篇文。<br />\n<br />\n現在的情況真係好嚴峻，一唔小心鬆懈左我地隨時會輸。大家係時候停止圍爐取暖打飛機; 要諗新的文宣手法去突破困局！ 單靠民間記者會我地好快就輸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDJucpJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDJucpJ.png&h=19542284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫巴打推: [正視聽] 乜你地真係覺得今日記者會，真係警察輸左咩？唔好咁天真啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430493</a><br />\n<br />\n今日會係第三日警察記者會，大家覺唔覺<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>開始習慣</strong></span>每日下午4點嘅犬隻恥笑大會? 沒有最on9，只有更on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。警方一開始所謂的澄稱、推連登撚狗Post和所謂的觀星[槍]實驗，根本係<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>有心比位人入去恥笑佢哋</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可能覺得自己都睇透左冇被影響，咁係因為你覺醒左;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">實際上好多人都仲只睇TVB真係會信被洗腦，由淺黃轉返左做中立覺得抗爭者暴力 (我朋友老母就係咁)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>。同埋我發現身邊已經開始有好多圍爐打飛機嘅情況發生，再打落去我地就輸撚緊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />琴晚嘅觀星團係好成功幫大家減壓，我絕對支持; 但真係間中玩一日就好，唔可以持久落去，否則只會變雨傘嘉年華2.0。<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家從今日起停止圍爐打飛機!</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間記者會我個人係極支持，係一個關鍵的抗衡手法; 但諗下觀眾會係邊個? 訊息係咪真係傳遞到比廣大市民? 答案係不能！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />CCTVB只會播4點鐘的記招。現時的文宣已經到瓶頸位 (例如9/8 和理飛根本就冇人知)，我地<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>必須諗新的文宣手法去做宣傳</strong></span>！小弟有少少睇法:<br />\n<br />\n1. 組團搞連續的18區放映會，另外搵人剪片(加字幕旁白配音); 內容盡量focus係民間記者會，黑警罪證及我地的訴求！連儂牆要繼續做，但已經開始麻木; 所以要播識郁嘅嘢先吸引到人圍觀注意！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WkXreB9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkXreB9.jpg&h=3f53db5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.&nbsp;全民文宣，人人有責。每日放工放學幫手派傳單、貼街招、幫電視轉台甚至人肉街招。我地要吸引到廣大市民的注意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOs3gQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOs3gQB.jpg&h=fadab2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.&nbsp;不定期的勇武抗爭必須繼續，唔可以比狗狗有休息的機會; 否則我地只會被清算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROr7JvJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROr7JvJ.jpg&h=727a4d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sT91NXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsT91NXu.jpg&h=c7aeac61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.&nbsp;9月之前，黎多次全港百萬人大遊行反映民意(此非終極一戰，但有巴打提出過。我知大家未必同意，我只係提出討論。搞的話可以考慮搵民陣吹雞，但行之前一個星期一定要集火瘋狂文宣！係所有人一齊做，不論前線定鍵盤戰士)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsWzovV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsWzovV.jpg&h=c3ce1383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後要幫推一下9/8和你飛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEaki4o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEaki4o.png&h=efdb09e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CLsJv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CLsJv4.jpg&h=464e7796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvJeowg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvJeowg.jpg&h=fd73e1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山，互相幫助<br />\n有禮貌，不分化，不割蓆(核彈都唔割)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"db55caaf4e46434d7597c53368113622b9c7f36c","tid":1430954,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:13:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79003dbc61a9882056050a2add0dbc412ce4ca4","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:16:06.000Z","msg":"推一推...."},{"pid":"08df4a6ba337756e54a0fa24c4da5099fb74347d","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"再推..."},{"pid":"3e503795bc2839a581692386e9c556f6db06aa4b","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"368d7485ce63058ddf0964e83a6a63dd80da3434","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"c9500f7c200546a0a9c9d9a13581545845b7872b","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"da918ace21abe99593c62d267133e9cb91c29dda","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:25:39.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"370d325bdf454cfe70ec173e701a6472f2507cd4","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-0