":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:50:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5882e40c61d9db43aac14b07f884be9c146a7429","tid":1430954,"uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab88ff46e6659ee0a95e56067d40f9f37a099e2f","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:12:29.000Z","msg":"對唔住，細佬反省過，一世唔會再做標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />懇求大家原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完巴打建議，決定重開一篇文。請各位無視我上一篇文。<br />\n<br />\n現在的情況真係好嚴峻，一唔小心鬆懈左我地隨時會輸。大家係時候停止圍爐取暖打飛機; 要諗新的文宣手法去突破困局！ 單靠民間記者會我地好快就輸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDJucpJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDJucpJ.png&h=19542284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫巴打推: [正視聽] 乜你地真係覺得今日記者會，真係警察輸左咩？唔好咁天真啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430493</a><br />\n<br />\n今日會係第三日警察記者會，大家覺唔覺<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>開始習慣</strong></span>每日下午4點嘅犬隻恥笑大會? 沒有最on9，只有更on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。警方一開始所謂的澄稱、推連登撚狗Post和所謂的觀星[槍]實驗，根本係<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>有心比位人入去恥笑佢哋</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可能覺得自己都睇透左冇被影響，咁係因為你覺醒左;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">實際上好多人都仲只睇TVB真係會信被洗腦，由淺黃轉返左做中立覺得抗爭者暴力 (我朋友老母就係咁)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>。同埋我發現身邊已經開始有好多圍爐打飛機嘅情況發生，再打落去我地就輸撚緊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />琴晚嘅觀星團係好成功幫大家減壓，我絕對支持; 但真係間中玩一日就好，唔可以持久落去，否則只會變雨傘嘉年華2.0。<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家從今日起停止圍爐打飛機!</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間記者會我個人係極支持，係一個關鍵的抗衡手法; 但諗下觀眾會係邊個? 訊息係咪真係傳遞到比廣大市民? 答案係不能！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />CCTVB只會播4點鐘的記招。現時的文宣已經到瓶頸位 (例如9/8 和理飛根本就冇人知)，我地<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>必須諗新的文宣手法去做宣傳</strong></span>！小弟有少少睇法:<br />\n<br />\n1. 組團搞連續的18區放映會，另外搵人剪片(加字幕旁白配音); 內容盡量focus係民間記者會，黑警罪證及我地的訴求！連儂牆要繼續做，但已經開始麻木; 所以要播識郁嘅嘢先吸引到人圍觀注意！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WkXreB9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkXreB9.jpg&h=3f53db5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.&nbsp;全民文宣，人人有責。每日放工放學幫手派傳單、貼街招、幫電視轉台甚至人肉街招。我地要吸引到廣大市民的注意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOs3gQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOs3gQB.jpg&h=fadab2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.&nbsp;不定期的勇武抗爭必須繼續，唔可以比狗狗有休息的機會; 否則我地只會被清算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROr7JvJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROr7JvJ.jpg&h=727a4d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sT91NXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsT91NXu.jpg&h=c7aeac61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.&nbsp;9月之前，黎多次全港百萬人大遊行反映民意(此非終極一戰，但有巴打提出過。我知大家未必同意，我只係提出討論。搞的話可以考慮搵民陣吹雞，但行之前一個星期一定要集火瘋狂文宣！係所有人一齊做，不論前線定鍵盤戰士)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsWzovV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsWzovV.jpg&h=c3ce1383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後要幫推一下9/8和你飛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEaki4o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEaki4o.png&h=efdb09e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CLsJv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CLsJv4.jpg&h=464e7796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvJeowg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvJeowg.jpg&h=fd73e1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山，互相幫助<br />\n有禮貌，不分化，不割蓆(核彈都唔割)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:52:32.000Z","msg":"文宣得閒嘅可考慮更新下維基百科，好多野都missing。<span style=\"color: red;\">有好多內容細節位（好似8月3-4日遊行），又或者比較細嘅行動（如公務員加入聯署、前高官支持五大訴求）都miss 咗冇人更新同理會。</span>網典仲update過佢其實好可悲。<br />\n<br />\n而且本身wiki靠果幾丁友去編輯，咁多事件都未必follow 得切。以往寫開果班完全潛哂水賴政治潔癖，一係就改小小野就算。<br />\n<br />\n不過最<span style=\"color: red;\">大問題係好多事件條目都冇「自由圖片」。</span>維基百科規定媒體作品一定要作商業用途同容許任何修改。基本上主流媒體、通訊社d相都禁止使用，會好快俾人刪除。而其他民間媒體（好似獨媒、Socrec)又唔肯將d相商業用其實好難搞。除非又聯署叫佢地學立場新聞facebook live咁無條件開放版權作任何用途，而且毋須通知先可以得。<br />\n<br />\n英文Wiki果面河蟹仲嚴重，班人共識規定每次遊行只可一小段，不可另開條目。之後又會叫你合併...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0&amp;mobileaction=toggle_view_desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fw%2Findex.php%3Ftitle%3DTemplate%3A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%26mobileaction%3Dtoggle_view_desktop&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=677dd156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0&amp;mobileaction=toggle_view_desktop</a>"},{"pid":"4c5a206479e38c46a82e27219f465c5b8d414017","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:02:39.000Z","msg":"push wiki"},{"pid":"54e053ffda75f3454979dc65cfebb4ee6c82895a","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae885fec063b402d2e7db89e055fca9fd2a50352","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"87314a233bd5af456214fc00d59c58295bf62af2","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"32f41788a1a65f5690fc78774a1f61cbfb5d4f2f","tid":1430954,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:22:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"044d0f4e84a43aefcef6b478015c3107160a357e","tid":1430954,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bc818926bc8af6a9e37bc2c4c2b54e055e7518f","tid":1430954,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"再推推"},{"pid":"f61eafe07417534f1909420864cfc8de7e4e0e20","tid":1430954,"uid":232949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:54:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9cc839a36d282dfd08635d8fa0eba661e2d5631","tid":1430954,"uid":232949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d3e93994eb85e744c008cccc00feb80dd43073","tid":1430954,"uid":232949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c82b0fad0981dde994755b99560cb2862745bbb","tid":1430954,"uid":232949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15aef16a62c61eb4a9cb535e7e119ed82021835d","tid":1430954,"uid":232949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:56:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"866641f614be843a0ef22f935bf2cc4d961f05d1","tid":1430954,"uid":211317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:58:01.000Z","msg":"推，我會去自己區派下傳單"},{"pid":"ed8068b191491277efd6dccbfc4f2784a243d864","tid":1430954,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bef35d770bef5abd99120154f3ab1092eec130","tid":1430954,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6aa9d1d8b2cf81c48b4555949764fafce9b90d0","tid":1430954,"uid":300032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738dbbfc6c253112e390f563cfc472b340004ff9","tid":1430954,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c31f84ffb3e320c3abbb37052079cc7df08d0160","tid":1430954,"uid":26910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:17:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5d9a65fcbe7af76ff207b6996e698fca89b25fa","tid":1430954,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:17:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我建議文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n已有23,799個簽名（8 Aug 2019 at 16:17）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n鼓勵遊行示威口號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"992395a60050f3902d378ad6e0810abe230b07b7","tid":1430954,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1a36e3adc9d39beac